        "text": "You are a senior HR screener. Evaluate this candidate for a Software Developer role.\n\nCandidate info already collected:\nName: {{ $('On form submission').item.json['What is your name'] }}\nEmail: {{ $('On form submission').item.json['What is your Email'] }}\nExperience: {{ $('On form submission').item.json['Do you have any experience?'] }}\nSkills: {{ $('On form submission').item.json['Tell us about your skills'] }}\nCover letter: {{ $('On form submission').item.json['Cover Letter (Optional)'] }}\n\nRequired skills: JavaScript, React, minimum 1 year experience\nNice to have: TypeScript, Node.js, automation tools\n\nRead the attached CV to verify and add to what we already know. Respond ONLY in raw JSON:\n{\n  \"score\": (0-100),\n  \"qualified\": (true or false),\n  \"strengths\": \"2-3 sentence summary\",\n  \"concerns\": \"1-2 sentence summary\",\n  \"recommended_action\": \"invite\" or \"reject\"\n}",
        "inputType": "binary",
        "binaryPropertyName": "=Upload_you_cv_here",
        "options": {}
